               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa gǝbrä ḥǝmāmāt “Book of the Rite of the Holy Week" (fols.
                     4ra-155rc)&#xD; I-1) Introduction (fols. 4ra-5vb)&#xD; I-2) Eve of Palm Sunday
                     (fols. 5vb-7vb)&#xD; I-3) Palm Sunday (fols. 7vb-13ra)&#xD; I-4) Monday (fols.
                     13ra-26vc)&#xD; I-5) Tuesday (fols. 26vc-40rb)&#xD; I-6) Wednesday (fols.
                     40rb-51rc)&#xD; I-7) Thursday (fols. 51rc-66vb)&#xD; I-8) Friday (fols.
                     67ra-121va)&#xD; I-9) Saturday (fols. 121va-144ra), including: Rāʾǝya Yoḥannǝs
                     "Revelation of John" (fols. 124ra-133vc); Tǝmhǝrta ḫǝbuʾāt “Teaching of
                     Mysteries” (fols. 140vb-142ra)&#xD; I-10) Homily by Cyriacus of Behnesa [Lāḥā
                     Māryām “Lamentation of Mary”] (fols. 145ra-155rc)&#xD; &#xD; Additiones
                     1-2.</summary>
